flowRoot.flowPara: f is focal distance from intrinsics.xml (default 545 px)
x1,x2,y1,y2 are from the bounding box of the contour in px
r is the radius of the sphere (2.25 cm)
Calculated (once for x, once for y):
alpha, theta, phi, and psi are angles (match triangle colours)
L is the distance of the sphere center to the focal point in cm.
z is the distance of the sphere from the sensor plane in cm.
x is the distance of the sphere from the principal axis in cm.
